 $\\delta\\simeq0.4-0.5$ if convection is included\nin the fit. Furthermore, we find that the use of the AMS-02 Beryllium data\nprovides a lower limit on the vertical size of the Galactic propagation halo of\n$z_\\mathrm{h}\\gtrsim3$ kpc.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Mar 2021 18:00:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 17 Jun 2021 14:52:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-18"}
