 of 2.5 mins/plan with SA, and less than 3 seconds without\nSA. Compared to this, manual planning at our centre takes around 20 mins/plan.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 Mar 2021 03:02:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-10"}
