ormed by four cascaded\nMAJ gates WP increases the throughput by 3.6x.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 Mar 2021 10:57:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 21 Jun 2021 14:05:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-22"}
