ark-matter from the stellar component in SGs. b.\nCompact elliptical SG formation.\n  An assembly of these results and others are presented in a fast and robust\ncatalog.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 Mar 2021 13:54:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-19"}
