 discovered, where does that exoplanet stand in its\nevolution towards life as we have it on Earth nowadays, or beyond? In this\npaper we provide mathematical criteria to answer this question within the\nframework of the Evo-SETI Theory, thus creating the EVO-SETI SCALE.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Mar 2021 22:50:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-22"}
